{"tid":2297924,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【嫖客確診】鳳姐﹕可唔戴罩做","createTime":"2020-11-23T15:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T16:34:52.000Z","uid":66271,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cc4e46aa35a2a29e677ff82a61fa61a47a4b51a1","tid":2297924,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T15:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201123/407677776682815488876429.jpeg/mOSO9YFParRGTSLvjeOKlF9oz_sjGCpXic4kSonOJEo?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201123%2F407677776682815488876429.jpeg%2FmOSO9YFParRGTSLvjeOKlF9oz_sjGCpXic4kSonOJEo%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=4d9b1e5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者今晚到亞皆老街及花園街交界建興大廈了解，發現由5樓至13樓每一樓層均有鳳樓，但部分疑因疫情關係沒有營業，故顯得疏落，全幢共約有20間鳳樓仍營業，大多正在工作。部分鳳樓門外貼有招客的宣傳字眼，當中亦有提醒客人要戴口罩的告示﹕「為己為人，請戴口罩，no mask，沒口罩者，no sexy！恕不招待！」<br />\n<br />\n記者嘗試向一些鳳姐了解情況，她們應門時均沒有戴上口罩，操鄉音透露近日沒有警員或衛生署人員上門呼籲她們接受檢測。記者問及工作時會否戴上口罩，有鳳姐稱﹕「可以唔戴口罩做。」記者在現場亦發現有嫖客「洗樓」尋找可光顧的鳳姐。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，昨晚深夜（22日）有人發現多名身穿保護衣人士到建興大廈了解，估計當時是嘗試尋找確診35歲男子曾光顧的鳳姐，惟因確診男子報稱忘記曾到訪的樓層及單位，最終局方人員未能找到該名鳳姐。至今日凌晨警方及衞生署人員再上樓呼籲其他鳳姐接受檢測。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，自從著名尋歡「性」地尖沙咀香檳大廈被收購後，旺角建興大廈成為區內近年出名的鳳廈。建興大廈樓高14層，樓齡超過50年，其中12層200多個劏房單位，被用作「一樓一鳳」，曾有各國佳麗進駐。警方於2018年1月曾在上址進行掃黃行動，拘捕99名妓女，包括來自中國內地、俄羅斯、烏克蘭、泰國等地的妓女，其中包括7名變性人。惟警方大舉掃黃後，建興大廈的黃色事業食舊繁盛，警方同年7月曾再掃黃拘68名涉嫌賣淫的中外女子及12名泰籍變性人。記者今晚曾嘗試在著名的黃色網頁搜索建興大廈的性工作者資料，卻發現沒有建興大廈在鳳樓名單內，未知是否有人將相關資料刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201123/407667945892745216312065.jpeg/89bUXHkoVAMNnX_OGIBlrtL7xkABFMosQt7232je9t8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201123%2F407667945892745216312065.jpeg%2F89bUXHkoVAMNnX_OGIBlrtL7xkABFMosQt7232je9t8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7a6b6f02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5442476a1249170a83ba6d6e28e42f89975b8d5","tid":2297924,"uid":89064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T15:55:10.000Z","msg":"可以唔戴口罩(打車輪)"},{"pid":"d08cf31e1662a99688ecb9592af5d31a825d2867","tid":2297924,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T15:56:26.000Z","msg":"唔戴罩咁撚淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf19e6220a9155998c089462994ac86cd1ac5cd9","tid":2297924,"uid":271945,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T15:57:32.000Z","msg":"古有環保吹，今有環保做<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4e5c24951f1449c18325274f78e569f941359c","tid":2297924,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T16:01:21.000Z","msg":"變性人。。。。"},{"pid":"c37ab7ada548bb1d2775ce6a3549eb2c9deab87f","tid":2297924,"uid":5008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T16:03:04.000Z","msg":"睇錯可以唔帶套做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f3bfab9b7ff4abd38da2c3c48bb025f0bf1fdd","tid":2297924,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a4e5c24951f1449c18325274f78e569f941359c","tid":2297924,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T16:01:21.000Z","msg":"變性人。。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T16:04:53.000Z","msg":"幸運大抽獎，邊個咁唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738c40d241d7b19f73814b5119d04379d80511c0","tid":2297924,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T16:07:14.000Z","msg":"咁能多變性人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係有market?"},{"pid":"05fb4d95dab8bec3ae6936558e7b82c288aee92d","tid":2297924,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T16:07:58.000Z","msg":"掃黃時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10c4a3ea3eeda51329b789ae32df91f91fe393b","tid":2297924,"uid":50218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor